@EngineApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5086
@DemoTenantAlpha = A1A1A1A1-A1A1-A1A1-A1A1-A1A1A1A1A1A1
@DemoTenantBeta = B2B2B2B2-B2B2-B2B2-B2B2-B2B2B2B2B2B2

// A variável abaixo captura o ID da avaliação gerada no POST automaticamente
@EvaluationId = {{createNewEvaluation.response.headers.X-Evaluation-Id}}

### 1. Criar uma nova Avaliação (Exemplo: Precisa AUMENTAR cobertura)
# @name createNewEvaluation
POST {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: test-demo-idempotency-key-001

{
  "personalContext": {
    "age": 35,
    "maritalStatus": "CASADO",
    "professionRiskLevel": "MEDIO",
    "isSmoker": false
  },
  "financialContext": {
    "monthlyIncome": {
      "exactValue": 12000
    },
    "emergencyFundMonths": 1,
    "debts": {
      "totalAmount": 150000,
      "remainingTermMonths": 48
    },
    "currentLifeInsurance": {
      "coverageAmount": 50000,
      "policyType": "TEMPORARIO"
    }
  },
  "familyContext": {
    "dependentsCount": 2,
    "dependentsAges": [5, 8]
  },
  "operationalData": {
    "originChannel": "SITE_CORRETORA",
    "hasExplicitActiveConsent": true,
    "consentId": "lgpd-term-12345",
    "tenantId": "{{DemoTenantAlpha}}"
  }
}

### 2. Testar Idempotência (Execute esta chamada logo em seguida)
# Você verá que ela retorna a mesma resposta sem recalcular ou duplicar no banco.
POST {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: test-demo-idempotency-key-001

{
  "personalContext": { "age": 35, "maritalStatus": "CASADO", "professionRiskLevel": "MEDIO", "isSmoker": false },
  "financialContext": { "monthlyIncome": { "exactValue": 12000 }, "emergencyFundMonths": 1, "debts": { "totalAmount": 150000 }, "currentLifeInsurance": { "coverageAmount": 50000 } },
  "familyContext": { "dependentsCount": 2 },
  "operationalData": { "originChannel": "SITE_CORRETORA", "hasExplicitActiveConsent": true, "consentId": "lgpd-term-12345", "tenantId": "{{DemoTenantAlpha}}" }
}

### 3. Testar erro de LGPD (Consentimento Falso = Error 422)
POST {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: erro-lgpd-test-01

{
  "personalContext": { "age": 30, "maritalStatus": "SOLTEIRO", "professionRiskLevel": "BAIXO", "isSmoker": false },
  "financialContext": { "monthlyIncome": { "exactValue": 5000 } },
  "familyContext": { "dependentsCount": 0 },
  "operationalData": {
    "originChannel": "APP",
    "hasExplicitActiveConsent": false,
    "consentId": "nao-aceitou",
    "tenantId": "{{DemoTenantAlpha}}"
  }
}

### 4. Consultar Avaliação Criada (Puxando o ID gerado no passo 1)
GET {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/evaluations/{{EvaluationId}}
Accept: application/json


### 5. Verificar Integridade Criptográfica (Auditoria Admin)
GET {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/audit/evaluations/{{EvaluationId}}/verify
Accept: application/json


### 6. Consultar Relatório do Piloto (DemoTenantAlpha)
GET {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/reports/pilot?tenantId={{DemoTenantAlpha}}
Accept: application/json


### 7. Verões do Motor Ativas
GET {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/engine/versions
Accept: application/json


### 8. Limpar o Ambiente Demo (Deletar dados do DemoTenantAlpha)
DELETE {{EngineApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/demo-environments/tenants/{{DemoTenantAlpha}}
Accept: application/json
